---
---

<section class="coach-section" id="coach">
  <div class="coach-wrap">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:56px">
      <span class="sec-label">Coach IA Personnalisé</span>
      <h2>Une IA qui te connaît.<br /><em>Vraiment.</em></h2>
      <p class="sec-sub" style="max-width:540px;margin:0 auto">
        Tous les journaux de trading analysent tes stats.
        MyTradingCoach est le seul à analyser tes stats
        <strong>en connaissant ta stratégie</strong>.
        C'est la différence entre un robot et un coach.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Comparaison avant/après -->
    <div class="coach-compare reveal">
      <div class="coach-col bad">
        <div class="coach-col-label">
          <span class="coach-col-ic bad-ic">✗</span>
          Analyse générique
        </div>
        <div class="coach-bubble bad-bubble">
          <div class="coach-avatar bad-av">🤖</div>
          <div class="coach-msg">
            <p>
              "Attention — tu as pris <strong>18 trades aujourd'hui</strong>.
              C'est élevé et peut indiquer du overtrading.
              Essaie de limiter tes entrées et d'être plus sélectif."
            </p>
            <span class="coach-tag bad-tag">Conseil inutile</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="coach-col-note">
          Sans contexte, l'IA confond ta stratégie avec un problème.
          18 trades/jour c'est peut-être ta norme.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="coach-divider">
        <div class="coach-divider-line"></div>
        <div class="coach-divider-vs">VS</div>
        <div class="coach-divider-line"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="coach-col good">
        <div class="coach-col-label">
          <span class="coach-col-ic good-ic">✓</span>
          Coach personnalisé
        </div>
        <div class="coach-bubble good-bubble">
          <div class="coach-avatar good-av">🎯</div>
          <div class="coach-msg">
            <p>
              "Tes <strong>18 trades aujourd'hui</strong> sont dans ta norme
              de scalper ICT. Ce qui attire l'attention :
              <strong>6 de tes 7 pertes</strong> sont survenues entre 15h-16h NY,
              sur des OB que le price avait déjà visités.
              Évite les re-entrées sur OB invalidés après le London close."
            </p>
            <span class="coach-tag good-tag">Conseil actionnable</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="coach-col-note">
          L'IA connaît ton profil. Elle analyse dans le bon contexte
          et détecte ce qui compte vraiment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 3 étapes en cartes -->
    <div class="steps-wrap reveal">

      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-card-top">
          <span class="step-badge">01</span>
          <div class="step-icon">⚡</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="step-card-title">Tu définis ton profil</h3>
        <p class="step-card-desc">
          Style, stratégie, sessions, fréquence normale.
          5 minutes. Une fois. L'IA sait tout avant d'analyser.
        </p>
        <div class="step-card-tags">
          <span class="step-tag-pill style">⚡ Scalping</span>
          <span class="step-tag-pill strat">ICT</span>
          <span class="step-tag-pill strat">Order Blocks</span>
          <span class="step-tag-pill session">📍 London</span>
          <span class="step-tag-pill strat">FVG</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step-arrow-h" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="40" height="16" viewBox="0 0 40 16" fill="none">
          <path d="M0 8h36M30 2l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="step-arrow-v" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="16" height="40" viewBox="0 0 16 40" fill="none">
          <path d="M8 0v36M2 30l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-card-top">
          <span class="step-badge">02</span>
          <div class="step-icon">📖</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="step-card-title">Tu journalises tes trades</h3>
        <p class="step-card-desc">
          30 secondes par trade. L'IA connaît ton contexte —
          elle sait interpréter chaque entrée sans jugement hors sujet.
        </p>
        <div class="step-trade-preview">
          <div class="step-trade-row">
            <span class="trade-pill long">LONG</span>
            <span class="trade-asset">MES</span>
            <span class="trade-meta">London · 8h32</span>
            <span class="trade-pnl pos">+$225</span>
          </div>
          <div class="step-trade-row">
            <span class="trade-pill short">SHORT</span>
            <span class="trade-asset">NQ</span>
            <span class="trade-meta">NY · 15h10</span>
            <span class="trade-pnl neg">-$180</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step-arrow-h" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="40" height="16" viewBox="0 0 40 16" fill="none">
          <path d="M0 8h36M30 2l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="step-arrow-v" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="16" height="40" viewBox="0 0 16 40" fill="none">
          <path d="M8 0v36M2 30l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="step-card step-card-accent">
        <div class="step-card-top">
          <span class="step-badge active">03</span>
          <div class="step-icon">🎯</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="step-card-title">L'IA t'analyse <em>vraiment</em></h3>
        <p class="step-card-desc">
          Debrief hebdo, insights quotidiens, objectifs —
          tout adapté à ta stratégie. Pas à un trader fictif.
        </p>
        <div class="step-insight-pill">
          <span class="insight-dot"></span>
          "6 pertes sur 7 entre 15h–16h NY sur OB invalidés"
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>


    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="coach-cta reveal">
      <a href="https://app.mytradingcoach.app/register" class="btn-p">
        Créer mon profil trader gratuitement
        <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <p class="coach-cta-note">Gratuit sans CB · Premium : essai 7 jours, aucun prélèvement avant</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .coach-section {
    padding: 100px 5%;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .coach-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(59,130,246,.06) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .coach-wrap { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }

  /* Comparaison */
  .coach-compare {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }

  .coach-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }

  .coach-col-label {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--txt2);
    font-family: var(--mono); letter-spacing: .3px;
  }

  .coach-col-ic {
    width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .bad-ic  { background: rgba(239,68,68,.15); color: #ef4444; }
  .good-ic { background: rgba(16,185,129,.15); color: #10b981; }

  .coach-bubble {
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px;
    display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .bad-bubble  { background: rgba(239,68,68,.05); border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.15); }
  .good-bubble { background: rgba(16,185,129,.05); border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.2); }

  .coach-avatar {
    width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .bad-av  { background: rgba(239,68,68,.1); }
  .good-av { background: rgba(16,185,129,.1); }

  .coach-msg { flex: 1; }
  .coach-msg p { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--txt2); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .coach-msg p strong { color: var(--txt); }

  .coach-tag {
    font-size: 10px; font-family: var(--mono); padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 100px; font-weight: 600;
  }
  .bad-tag  { background: rgba(239,68,68,.1); color: #ef4444; }
  .good-tag { background: rgba(16,185,129,.1); color: #10b981; }

  .coach-col-note {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--txt3); line-height: 1.5;
    font-style: italic; padding: 0 4px;
  }

  .coach-divider {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding-top: 48px;
  }
  .coach-divider-line {
    width: 1px; height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, var(--b2), transparent);
  }
  .coach-divider-vs {
    font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--txt3);
    background: var(--bg3); border: 1px solid var(--b2);
    padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 6px; letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  /* ── 3 cartes étapes ── */
  .steps-wrap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .step-card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--b);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;
    height: 100%; transition: border-color .2s, transform .2s;
  }
  .step-card:hover { border-color: var(--b2); transform: translateY(-3px); }
  .step-card-accent {
    border-color: rgba(59,130,246,.3);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--card), rgba(59,130,246,.04));
  }
  .step-card-accent:hover { border-color: var(--blue); }
  .step-card-top { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
  .step-badge {
    font-size: 10px; font-family: var(--mono); font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--blue2);
    background: rgba(59,130,246,.1); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.2);
    padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 100px;
  }
  .step-badge.active { background: var(--blue); color: #fff; border-color: var(--blue); }
  .step-icon { font-size: 22px; }
  .step-card-title {
    font-family: var(--disp); font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--txt); letter-spacing: -.2px; line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .step-card-title em { color: var(--blue2); font-style: normal; }
  .step-card-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--txt2); line-height: 1.65; flex: 1; }
  .step-card-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .step-tag-pill {
    font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono);
    padding: 2px 9px; border-radius: 100px; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .step-tag-pill.style { background: rgba(34,211,238,.08); color: var(--pulse); border: 1px solid rgba(34,211,238,.15); }
  .step-tag-pill.strat { background: rgba(59,130,246,.08); color: var(--blue2); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.15); }
  .step-tag-pill.session { background: rgba(16,185,129,.08); color: #10b981; border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.15); }
  .step-trade-preview { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .step-trade-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: var(--bg3); border: 1px solid var(--b);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 7px 10px; font-size: 11px;
  }
  .trade-pill { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .trade-pill.long  { background: rgba(16,185,129,.15); color: #10b981; }
  .trade-pill.short { background: rgba(239,68,68,.15); color: #ef4444; }
  .trade-asset { font-family: var(--mono); font-weight: 600; color: var(--txt); }
  .trade-meta  { color: var(--txt3); flex: 1; }
  .trade-pnl   { font-family: var(--mono); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .trade-pnl.pos { color: #10b981; }
  .trade-pnl.neg { color: #ef4444; }
  .step-insight-pill {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px;
    font-size: 11px; font-style: italic; color: var(--txt2);
    background: rgba(59,130,246,.06); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.15);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .insight-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--blue2); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--blue);
  }
  .step-arrow-h {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: var(--b2); padding: 0 12px; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .step-arrow-v { display: none; }


  /* CTA */
  .coach-cta { text-align: center; }

  .btn-p {
    background: var(--blue); color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 10px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(59,130,246,.4);
    transition: background .2s, transform .2s, box-shadow .2s; font-family: var(--disp);
  }
  .btn-p:hover { background: var(--blue2); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .coach-cta-note {
    margin-top: 12px; font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--txt3); font-family: var(--mono);
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .coach-section { padding: 60px 16px; }
    .coach-compare { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .coach-divider { flex-direction: row; padding-top: 0; }
    .coach-divider-line { width: 60px; height: 1px; }
    .steps-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0; }
    .step-arrow-h { display: none; }
    .step-arrow-v { display: flex; justify-content: center; color: var(--b2); padding: 8px 0; }
    .step-card { height: auto; }
  }
</style>
